<div class="calendaria chat-release">
  <div class="release-header">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar"></i>
    <strong>{{localize "CALENDARIA.Release.Title" version=version}}</strong>
  </div>

  <div class="release-body">
    <p class="release-patreon">
      <strong><a href="https://www.patreon.com/3deathsaves" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i
            class="fa-brands fa-patreon"></i> Now on Patreon!</a></strong>
      All current modules stay free!
    </p>

    <h4>New</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Weather Picker gear button to open Weather settings</li>
      <li>API: <code>timestampToDate</code> returns ordinal, monthName, intercalary</li>
      <li>API: <code>dateToTimestamp</code> accepts ordinal-based month lookup</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Fixes</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Temperature of 0 no longer treated as empty</li>
      <li>"Disable Weather FX" respected on day change</li>
      <li>Weather sounds work without FXMaster and use Environment volume</li>
      <li>Forecast wind speeds stable across re-renders</li>
      <li>Multi-year periodic seasons cycle correctly</li>
      <li>Extreme wind speed reduced to realistic 250 kph</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <a class="open-note" href="{{repoUrl}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square"></i> {{localize "CALENDARIA.Release.ReleaseNotes"}}
  </a>
</div>
